Create Measures 12

Note: Please follow the following gif  to create the Calculated Measures table and then create the measures using the formulas down below



Calculating Measures

SumCases = SUM('STD Cases'[STD Cases])

CounCases = COUNT('STD Cases'[STD Cases])

Current Year Cases = CALCULATE([.SumCases], DATESYTD(DimDate[Date]))

Cases LY = CALCULATE([.Current Year Cases], SAMEPERIODLASTYEAR(DimDate[Date]))

Diff Cases = [.Current Year Cases]-'STD Cases'[.Cases LY]

Cases Per 100K = ('STD Cases'[.SumCases] / 'STD Cases'[.#Population])*100000

YoY = (DIVIDE([.Current Year Cases], [.Cases LY],0)-1)
